{"type":null,"faqId":44865,"title":"语音唤醒怎么使用","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.s2{display: inline-block; text-indent: 0; min-width: 0.19444445in;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p2{text-indent:0.29166666in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n.p3{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:11pt;}\n.p4{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:center;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n.p5{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Arial;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">语音唤醒默认是关闭的，请在“设置 &gt; 智能辅助 &gt; 语音唤醒“下，开启语音唤醒开关。进行简单的设置和语音训练后，就可以使用语音唤醒功能了。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">目前语音唤醒主要支持两类功能：</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span class=\"s1\">语音找手机，您可以说“你好，小E，你在哪儿”</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s2\">1.  </span><span class=\"s1\">语音打电话，您可以说“你好，小E，打电话给小华”</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">提醒： 如果只说“你好，小E”的话，只会亮起屏幕，并不会有提示音； 只有再说“你在哪儿”或“打电话给XXX”时，才会有提示音和进一步的动作；</span>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161818\" style=\"width:2.59375in;height:4.5909724in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161819\" style=\"width:2.6034722in;height:4.5902777in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p4\">\n<img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161820\" style=\"width:2.5951388in;height:4.5979166in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/><img src=\"http://consumer.huawei.com/support/servlet/imageServlet?dlType=HtmlAreaImage&imageId=161821\" style=\"width:2.6034722in;height:4.5902777in;vertical-align:text-bottom;\"/></p>\n<p class=\"p5\">\n<span>* 图示仅供参考，具体操作请以手机实际界面为准。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":144,"faqType":"其他","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"366","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442409273000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":5,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"语音唤醒,使用","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}